parameters.name: X
parameters.description:
Distance from the Earth along the            
      Earth-Sun line, positive towards the Sun, in units of Re.

parameters.name: Y_GSE
parameters.description:
Distance from the Earth along the            
      dawn-dusk meridian, positive towards dusk, in units of Re.

parameters.name: Z_GSE
parameters.description:
Distance from the Earth above or below       
      the ecliptic plane (positive 'northwards') in units of Re.

parameters.name: Y_GSM
parameters.description:
Distance from the Earth along the GSM        
      Y-direction in units of Re.

parameters.name: Z_GSM
parameters.description:
Distance from the Earth along the GSM        
      Z-direction in units of Re.
